<div class="col-lg-12  margin-top-double">
    <h1 class="grey ">Arduino</h1>
    <hr>
</div>

<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-3 col-lg-3 padding-top">
    <img src="{{@unit.publicUri}}/images/ardunio-icon.png" class="img-responsive">
</div>

<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8 col-lg-8 padding-top">

</div>

<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-9 col-lg-9 padding-top">
    <h3 class="uppercase">它是做什么的</h3>
    <hr>
    <p class="grey margin-top">将Arduino UNO板连接到WSO2 IoT Server并可视化传感器数据。</p>
    <br>
    <h3 class="uppercase">你需要什么</h3>
    <hr>
    <ul class="list-unstyled">
        <li class="padding-top-double">
            <span class="badge">第 01 项</span>
            Arduino UNO 板。
        </li>
        <li>
            <span class="badge">第 02 项</span>
          	给 Arduino的部件 WiFi Shield。
        </li>
        <li>
            <span class="badge">第 03 项</span>
            LED灯泡连接到引脚13.如果您没有LED灯泡，请使用Arduino板上的灯泡。 板上的一个默认连接到引脚13。
        </li>
        <li>
            <span class="badge">第 04 项</span>
            	电阻 (如 330 欧姆)
        </li>
        <li>
            <span class="badge">步骤 05</span>
           	 接下来，转到[准备]部分。去掉步骤5，因为这是所有其他项目的唯一步骤。
    </ul>
    <br>
    <a href="/api-store/apis/info?name={{@uriParams.deviceType}}&version=1.0.0&provider=admin"
       class="btn-operations" target="_blank">
        <i class="fw fw-api add-margin-1x"></i> 查看 API
    </a>
    <a href="#" class="download-link btn-operations">
        <i class="fw fw-download add-margin-1x"></i>下载 缩略图
    </a>
    <p class="doc-link">点击 <a href="https://docs.wso2.com/display/IoTS320/Arduino"
                                 target="_blank">这</a> 了解最新的指示和故障排除。</p>
    <div id="download-device-modal-content" class="hide">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-7  center-container">
                    <h3>为您的设备命名并从以下链接下载代理。</h3>
                    <br/>
                    <form id="downloadForm" method="GET"
                          action="{{@app.context}}/api/devices/sketch/download">
                        <div id="invalid-username-error-msg" class="alert alert-danger hidden"
                             role="alert">
                            <i class="icon fw fw-error"></i><span></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="control-group">
                            <div class="controls">
                                <input class="new-device-name" style="color:#3f3f3f;padding:5px"
                                       type="text"
                                       placeholder="如 Home_Arduino"
                                       name="deviceName" size="60" required>
                                <br/><br/>
                                <input type="hidden" class="deviceType" name="deviceType"
                                       value="{{@uriParams.deviceType}}"/>
                                <input type="hidden" class="sketchType" name="sketchType"
                                       value="{{@uriParams.deviceType}}"/>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="buttons" style="padding-bottom: 0px">
                            <a class="btn btn-operations" onclick="downloadAgent()">
                               	 现在下载
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="device-agent-downloading-content" class="hide">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-7 col-centered center-container">
                    <h3>设备代理将很快下载。</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="device-400-content" class="hide">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-7 col-centered center-container">
                    <h3>后台异常。请稍后重试。</h3>
                    <div class="buttons">
                        <a href="#" id="device-400-link" class="btn-operations">
                           	 好的
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="device-401-content" class="hide">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-7 col-centered center-container">
                    <h3>你必须先登录。</h3><br/>
                    <div class="buttons">
                        <a href="#" id="device-401-link" class="blue-button">
                           	转到登录页面
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" onclick="hidePopup();" class="btn-operations">
                            	取消
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="device-403-content" class="hide">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-7 col-centered center-container">
                    <h3>操作不允许。</h3><br/>
                    <div class="buttons">
                        <a href="#" id="device-403-link" class="btn-operations">
                            	好的
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="device-409-content" class="hide">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-7 col-centered center-container">
                    <h3>设备程序不存在。</h3><br/>
                    <div class="buttons">
                        <a href="#" id="device-409-link" class="btn-operations">
                            	好的
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="device-unexpected-error-content" class="hide">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-7 col-centered center-container">
                    <h3>异常错误。</h3><br/>
                    <div class="buttons">
                        <a href="#" id="device-unexpected-error-link" class="btn-operations">
                            	好的
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <br/><br/>
</div>

<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 padding-double grey-bg">
    <h3 class="uppercase">准备</h3>
    <hr>
    <ul class="list-unstyled">
        <li class="padding-top-double">
            <span class="badge">01</span>
            	将WiFi shield安装到 Arduino UNO 板。
        </li>
        <li class="padding-top-double">
            <span class="badge">02</span>
            	连接到Arduino的LED灯泡，如下图所示：
            <br/><br/>
            <a href="{{@unit.publicUri}}/images/schematicsGuide.jpg" target="_blank">
                <img src="{{@unit.publicUri}}/images/schematicsGuide.jpg" class="img-responsive">
            </a>
            <br/>
        </li>

        <li class="padding-top-double">            <span class="badge">03</span>
            	点击 [Download Sketch] 以上下载Arduino程序。
        </li>
        <li class="padding-top-double">
            <span class="badge">04</span>
           	 解压下载的Arduino代理。
        </li>
        <li class="padding-top-double">
            <span class="badge">05</span>
            按名称ArduinoBoardSketch创建一个文件夹，并将下载的代理和源文件移动到该文件夹中。
        </li>
        <li class="padding-top-double">
            <span class="badge">06</span>
            	打开ArduinoBoardSketch.h文件并为其提供值
            <i>[WLAN_SSID]</i>,
            <i>[WLAN_PASS]</i>,
            <i>[SERVICE_PORT]</i>,
            <i>[server]</i> and
            <i>[deviceIP]</i>
           	 设备连接到WiFi网络的变量。
        </li>
        <li class="padding-top-double">
            <span class="badge">07</span>
           	  烧程序到Arduino板上并让程序运行。
        </li>
        <li class="padding-top-double">

            <span class="fw-stack margin-right">
                <i class="fw fw-circle-outline fw-stack-2x"></i>
                <i class="fw fw-right-arrow fw-stack-1x"></i>
            </span>
            	Arduino将向WSO2物联网服务器发送其内部温度。
            <br/><br/>

            <span class="fw-stack margin-right">
                <i class="fw fw-circle-outline fw-stack-2x"></i>
                <i class="fw fw-right-arrow fw-stack-1x"></i>
            </span>
            	通过设备管理页面控制在引脚13上的LED灯。
        </li>
    </ul>
    <br>
</div>

<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 padding-double">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-6 padding-double">
            <h3 class="uppercase">尝试</h3>
            <hr>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li class="padding-top-double">
                    <span class="badge">01</span>
                    	查看您的所有连接设备 <a href="{{@app.context}}/devices"> [设备管理] </a>页面。
                </li>
                <li class="padding-top-double">
                    <span class="badge">02</span>
                    	试用连接设备上的控制操作并监控实时数据。
                </li>
                <li class="padding-top-double">
                    <span class="badge">03</span>
                    	我们需要这一步吗？ 是否支持？
                </li>
            </ul>
            <br/>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-6 padding-double">
            <p class="grey margin-top">点击图片放大</p>
            <center>
                <a href="{{@unit.publicUri}}/images/myDevices_analytics.png" target="_blank">
                    <img src="{{@unit.publicUri}}/images/myDevices_analytics.png"
                         class="img-responsive">
                </a>
            </center>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div id="arduino-statistic-response-template" style="display: none">
    <div class="content">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-6 col-centered">
                <h3>
                    <span class="fw-stack">
                        <i class="fw fw-circle-outline fw-stack-2x"></i>
                        <i id="status-icon" class="fw fw-error fw-stack-1x"></i>
                    </span>
                    <br>
                </h3>
                <h4>
                    <span id="title"></span>
                    <br>
                </h4>
                <span id="description"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

